							cash (e.g., car, shares of stock, cash deposits)
						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<p>
							Assets may be used to store wealth, create income, and reduce
							future expenses.
						</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
			<li>
				<p>
					<TextStyle setType={'strong emphasis'}>Types of Assets</TextStyle>
				</p>
				<ul>
