						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<p>
							Household assets are items normally owned by a household, such as
							a home, a car, and furniture.
						</p>
					</li>
					<li>
						<p>
							Financial assets (i.e., investment), such as bonds, stocks, mutual
							funds, and real estate
						</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
