		</SubSection>
		<SubSection title='Positive Versus Negative Net Worth'>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<p>Positive net worth:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<p>When assets &gt; liabilities, net worth &gt; 0.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>Keep doing what you are doing.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>Do not forget that a person’s net worth fluctuates.</p>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p>Negative net worth:</p>
					<ul>
						<li>
							<p>When assets &lt; liabilities, net worth &lt; 0.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>It is a sign that you need to increase your net worth.</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<p>Strategies:</p>
							<ul>
								<li>
									<p>Increase assets</p>
								</li>
								<li>
									<p>Decrease debt</p>
								</li>
								<li>
									<p>Or both</p>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</SubSection>
	</StaticContent>
