							setType={'highlight'}
							setHighlightColor={'green'}>
							inflows
						</TextStyle> are <TextStyle setType={'emphasis'}>greater</TextStyle>
						than cash <TextStyle
							setType={'highlight'}
							setHighlightColor={'red'}>
							outflows
						</TextStyle>
					</p>
					<p>
						It means you have a <TextStyle setType={'strong emphasis'}>
							cash surplus
						</TextStyle> over a period of time, usually one month or one year.
					</p>
