					debit card
				</TextStyle>.
			</p>
			<StepsList>
				<li>
					<p>
						Open a checking account at a bank or credit union. When you open a
						checking account, <TextStyle setType={'highlight'}>
							you will typically receive a debit card
						</TextStyle>.
					</p>
					<dl>
						<dt>What is A Debit Card?</dt>
						<dd>
							<SideBySideImage
								imgName='debit-card.jpg'
								setRatio={'r4060'}
								setAlign={'alignRight'}>
								<p>Debit Cards:</p>
