											account(s) at a financial institution.
										</p>
									</li>
									<li>
										<p>
											are also known as bank cards, ATM cards, cash cards, and
											check cards.
										</p>
									</li>
									<li>
										<p>
											deduct money directly from your checking account to pay
											for a purchase.
										</p>
									</li>
									<li>
										<p>
