							<li>
								<p>
									Savings accounts have some limitations on how often you can
									withdraw funds.
								</p>
							</li>
							<li>
								<p>Savings accounts are safe.</p>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</li>

					<li>
						<p>Savings accounts help you store money for specific purposes.</p>
						<ul>
							<li>
								<p>
